  <entry>
    <title>Unity固定式虚拟摇杆</title>
    <link href="/2021/08/19/Unity%E5%9B%BA%E5%AE%9A%E5%BC%8F%E8%99%9A%E6%8B%9F%E6%91%87%E6%9D%86/"/>
    <url>/2021/08/19/Unity%E5%9B%BA%E5%AE%9A%E5%BC%8F%E8%99%9A%E6%8B%9F%E6%91%87%E6%9D%86/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="功能"><a href="#功能" class="headerlink" title="功能"></a>功能</h2><p>通过组件实现拖拽摇杆控制目标移动</p><div class="note note-secondary">            <p>部分变量功能见代码注释</p>          </div><h2 id="代码预览"><a href="#代码预览" class="headerlink" title="代码预览"></a>代码预览</h2><h3 id="VirtualJoystickControl组件"><a href="#VirtualJoystickControl组件" class="headerlink" title="VirtualJoystickControl组件"></a>VirtualJoystickControl组件</h3><figure class="highlight csharp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br><span class="line">54</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs csharp"><span class="hljs-keyword">using</span> System.Collections;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">using</span> System.Collections.Generic;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">using</span> UnityEngine;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">using</span> UnityEngine.EventSystems;<br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title">VirtualJoystickControl</span> : <span class="hljs-title">MonoBehaviour</span>, <span class="hljs-title">IPointerDownHandler</span>, <span class="hljs-title">IDragHandler</span>, <span class="hljs-title">IPointerUpHandler</span><br>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> RectTransform background;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> RectTransform handle;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">private</span> Canvas canvas;<br><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> Vector2 input;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">private</span> Vector2 radius;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">private</span> Vector2 position;<br><br>    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">Start</span>(<span class="hljs-params"></span>)</span><br>    &#123;<br>        canvas = GetComponentInParent&lt;Canvas&gt;();<br><br>        Vector2 center = <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> Vector2(<span class="hljs-number">0.5f</span>, <span class="hljs-number">0.5f</span>);<br>        background.pivot = center;<br>        handle.anchorMin = center;<br>        handle.anchorMax = center;<br>        handle.pivot = center;<br>        handle.anchoredPosition = Vector2.zero;<br><br>        position = Camera.main.WorldToScreenPoint(background.position);<br>        radius = background.sizeDelta / <span class="hljs-number">2</span>;<br>    &#125;<br><br>    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">OnPointerDown</span>(<span class="hljs-params">PointerEventData eventData</span>)</span><br>    &#123;<br>        OnDrag(eventData);<br>    &#125;<br><br>    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">OnDrag</span>(<span class="hljs-params">PointerEventData eventData</span>)</span><br>    &#123;<br>        input = (eventData.position - position) / (radius * canvas.scaleFactor);<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (input.magnitude &gt; <span class="hljs-number">0</span>)<br>        &#123;<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (input.magnitude &gt; <span class="hljs-number">1</span>)<br>                input = input.normalized;<br>        &#125;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span><br>            input = Vector2.zero;<br>        handle.anchoredPosition = input * radius;<br>    &#125;<br><br>    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">OnPointerUp</span>(<span class="hljs-params">PointerEventData eventData</span>)</span><br>    &#123;<br>        input = Vector2.zero;<br>        handle.anchoredPosition = Vector2.zero;<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="TargetObjectControl组件"><a href="#TargetObjectControl组件" class="headerlink" title="TargetObjectControl组件"></a>TargetObjectControl组件</h3><figure class="highlight csharp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs csharp"><span class="hljs-keyword">using</span> System.Collections;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">using</span> System.Collections.Generic;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">using</span> UnityEngine;<br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title">TargetObjectControl</span> : <span class="hljs-title">MonoBehaviour</span><br>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> VirtualJoystickControl virtualJoystickControl;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">private</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">float</span> speed = <span class="hljs-number">3</span>;<br><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">bool</span> changeDirection;<span class="hljs-comment">//选择此项会使TargetObject的方向与摇杆方向一致</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">bool</span> keepSpeedConstant;<span class="hljs-comment">//选择此项会使TargetObject的速度不受摇杆拖拽距离影响</span><br><br>    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">Update</span>(<span class="hljs-params"></span>)</span><br>    &#123;<br>        Vector2 input = virtualJoystickControl.input;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (changeDirection)<br>        &#123;<br>            transform.up = input.normalized;<br>        &#125;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (keepSpeedConstant)<br>        &#123;<br>            transform.Translate(input.normalized * Time.deltaTime * speed, Space.World);<br>        &#125;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span><br>        &#123;<br>            transform.Translate(<span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> Vector2(input.x, input.y) * Time.deltaTime * speed, Space.World);<br>        &#125;   <br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="下载"><a href="#下载" class="headerlink" title="下载"></a>下载</h2><h3 id="蓝奏云"><a href="#蓝奏云" class="headerlink" title="蓝奏云"></a>蓝奏云</h3><p>下载链接：<a href="https://wws.lanzoui.com/iyvPZsup8lc">https://wws.lanzoui.com/iyvPZsup8lc</a></p>]]></content>
    
    
